import { Component } from "@angular/core"; import { ActivatedRoute } from "@angular/router"; import { Course } from "src/app/models/course"; import { CourseService } from "src/app/services/course.service"; @Component({ selector: "app-course-detail", templateUrl: "./course-detail.component.html", styleUrls: ["./course-detail.component.css"], }) export class CourseDetailComponent { course: Course | undefined; constructor( private route: ActivatedRoute, private courseService: CourseService ) {} ngOnInit(): void { const id = Number(this.route.snapshot.paramMap.get("id")); if (id) { this.courseService.getCourses().subscribe((courses) => { this.course = courses.find((c) => c.id === id); }); } } }
